body_template.@value:
--- [Event Definition] ---------------------------

Alert Title                :       ${event_definition_title}
Alert Description          : ${event_definition_description}

--- [Event] --------------------------------------

Source                     :               ${event.source}
Priority                   :             ${event.priority}
Alert Time                 :            ${event.timestamp}
Message                    :              ${event.message}

Event ID                   : ${EventID}
Event ID                   : message.fields.EventID
Event ID                   : ${message.fields.EventID}
Who did it ?               : ${SubjectUserName}
Which user affected ?      : ${TargetUserName}
Source server/system       : ${source}



${foreach event.fields field}  ${field.key}: ${field.value}
${end}
${if backlog}
--- [Backlog] ------------------------------------
Last messages accounting for this alert:
${foreach backlog message}
${message}
${end}
${end}
